description:
Latent ~~~~> Displacement

Latent Displacement researches dimensional expressions navigating the latent space of a Compositional Pattern-Producing Network ( CPPN ). The generative piece explores the hidden beauty produced by the multi-dimensionality of a Recursive Neuronal Network.

On its default state, a new CPPN model is generated every ~5 seconds. By toggling randomization on the settings panel, the CPPN remains constant while altering two of its latent vectors sequentially.
